healpix-cxx (3.00-2) UNRELEASED; urgency=low

  * Remove compiler flag -march=native because it generates non-portable code.

 -- Leo Singer <leo.singer@ligo.org>  Wed, 30 Jan 2013 09:03:55 -0800

healpix-cxx (3.00-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * The C++ HEALPix library does not build on GCC 4.4. If the program 'g++' is
    present, but its version number is less than 4.5, then use 'g++-4.3'
    instead.

 -- Leo Singer <leo.singer@ligo.org>  Tue, 22 Jan 2013 08:59:59 -0800

